Title: An Act Changing the Name of Jose Abad Santos Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Felix G. Almano Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 745
An Act Changing the Name of Jose Abad Santos Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Felix G. Almano Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Jose Abad Santos Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, shall be changed to Felix G. Almano Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
